{
  "id": "RAW_2f9b18",
  "title": "OpenAI 深夜发布 3 个全新的语音模型，一手实测都在这了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/GjzPPANJktEE8HomAnTtIQ",
  "date": "2025-03-20 19:57:09",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI最近总是喜欢搞突袭。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨晚11点的时候突然发了一个预告，4秒钟的音频的大概意思，就是太平洋时间10点我们发个产品。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a48f8576-8b49-4bce-18ec-0941eb239700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8726968174204355\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"597\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186124\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a48f8576-8b49-4bce-18ec-0941eb239700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后就在北京时间凌晨1点，开了一场直播，发了一些新玩意。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">总结一下就是：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2个比Whisper更好的语音转文本的STT模型：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-transcribe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">和</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-transcribe</span></span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，1个文本生成语音的TTS模型 :</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-tts</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。这些模型都</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提供了API的接入方式。没了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个一个说。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">1. STT模型：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">gpt-4o-transcribe</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-transcribe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">和</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-transcribe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说是两个，其实也就是一个了，后者是前者的小参数版。</span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个模型的作用跟当年的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Whisper是一样的，跟大家在剪映里用的一键生成字幕的作用也是一样的，就是把一段语音，转成对应的正确的文本。</span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"51\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"500186152\" data-ratio=\"0.0881316098707403\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f260e0f-a82c-430e-1812-a861c6910000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1702\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f260e0f-a82c-430e-1812-a861c6910000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们一般把他们称为，STT（Speech-to-Text）模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个模型的核心，就是就是识别文字的准确率有多高，我相信大家在用剪映生成字幕的时候，一定会出现很多文字识别错误的情况，所以评判一个ASR模型效果咋样，就看正确率。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们的跑分是这样的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35c7f9c3-e0b4-42d7-b6f9-2f18d41d3d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5525800130633572\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1531\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186126\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35c7f9c3-e0b4-42d7-b6f9-2f18d41d3d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个是OpenAI的几个STT模型在FLEURS数据集上的词错率（Word Error Rate, WER）的对比表现。纵坐标表示词错率，越低代表模型的转录准确性越高；横坐标代表不同语言。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">词错率的意思就是用于衡量语音识别系统的准确性，它通过计算模型转录文本与人工参考文本之间的错误比例来得出，错得越少，WER越低，模型的表现也就越好。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">中文是从左往右数第五个，cmn，可以看到突出了一个小山丘，错误率一下子就都上来了，比隔壁几个都要高一些，中文还是难。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后那几个一柱擎天的语言都比较小众，比如bn是孟加拉语、mr是马拉地与、最高的那个ml是马拉雅拉姆语。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们除了跟自己比外，又放了一个跟别人家模型相比的图。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7bc0b73d-8a31-4ef9-7c6d-dda30ab01100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5571913929784824\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1766\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186127\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7bc0b73d-8a31-4ef9-7c6d-dda30ab01100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini是google的，scribe是Anthropic的，在对比的这些里面，确实达到了SOTA，但是不知道没比的模型里面，有没有比OpenAI更强的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我自己也做了一下实测，把我的两个口播视频去识别了一下，识别出来的效果在此，大家可以对比一下。标红的就是识别错误的地方。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/878524be-bf3f-4378-d7c7-3000ad6db100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47719762062128224\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1513\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186148\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/878524be-bf3f-4378-d7c7-3000ad6db100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a79bde58-66f6-4aa0-d575-dd1401d3c800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6203703703703703\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186153\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a79bde58-66f6-4aa0-d575-dd1401d3c800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实都大差不差，这么一看，GPT-4o-</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">mini-</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 3 [\\&quot;para\\&quot;,{\\&quot;tagName\\&quot;:\\&quot;section\\&quot;,\\&quot;attributes\\&quot;:{},\\&quot;namespaceURI\\&quot;:\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\&quot;}]&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">transcribe的性价比感觉非常突出。</span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT-4o-transcribe这个系列的两个模型，有一个蛮不错的特点，就是会自动清噪和去除非主线人物的语音识别。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如这个案例。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3907449268620967936\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3907449268620967936\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrSNRqXGZxc1erUoHIuN00d62exibFUkLgc2KicFia7sobnotRHVKHrdfGN7L72kyPNBRGfkxPZMkLxQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个片段是剪辑完的成片，所以有音乐，甚至在19秒以后，还有BGM里面的别人唱歌的声音，这些其实都是噪音，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT-4o-transcribe几乎全部剔除了，在整个转录里，我几乎没看到什么错误，除了把我的名字，卡兹克识别成了卡斯克。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我又试了一段粤语的，效果居然还可以，大致的好像是对的，就是细节这块我不太能验证了，有懂粤语的朋友可以看一下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6dec65ea-d2af-416c-3ae7-15811275d100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44722222222222224\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186154\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6dec65ea-d2af-416c-3ae7-15811275d100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后价格这块提一下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">gpt-4o-transcribe是每分钟大概$0.006，也就是人民币0.04元/分钟；</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-transcribe是</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每分钟大概$0.003，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也就是人民币0.02元/分钟.</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整体不算贵了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">2. TTS模型：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">gpt-4o-mini-tts</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI的一个新的TTS模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在英语效果和声音上，听了下，还算不错，不过毕竟这是国内，所以其实我更关注的是中文的生成效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我随手跑了一个，就，你们听听这个效果。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"openai-fm-coral-sincere\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=openai-fm-coral-sincere&amp;play_length=8%E7%A7%92\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"403.2\" source_size=\"403.2\" high_size=\"403.2\" play_length=\"8000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjY5ODAz\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrSNRqXGZxc1erUoHIuN00ds4qWutT1ichaBQ65U0QBohk9tKmI7CtzwfEvIa3Ir2qy2D4gd6wBuKA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">情绪什么的其实讲道理，还可以的，就是这个中文发音，真的一股子大佐味，这到底用的什么数据集啊。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">11Labs也有这个问题，中文根本没法听，太违和了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对比一下海螺（现在产品也更名叫Minimax了），他们的Audio生成出来的同文字的中文是这个效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"Minimax-1\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=Minimax-1&amp;play_length=8%E7%A7%92\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"139.5\" source_size=\"139.5\" high_size=\"139.5\" play_length=\"8000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjY5ODA0\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrSNRqXGZxc1erUoHIuN00dKy1Iugbo2H4icf6NlsELiaibzYx2WKTH9Q1eZcendWldr3bClLfJia8wQA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在发音上，根本就不是一个级别的，中国人的语音模型，还是得看中国制造。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">英语上，感觉很纯正，日语发音上，也感觉有点怪怪的。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"openai-fm-coral-cowboy&amp;nbsp;(1)\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=openai-fm-coral-cowboy%26nbsp%3B(1)&amp;play_length=16%E7%A7%92\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"764.1\" source_size=\"764.1\" high_size=\"764.1\" play_length=\"16000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjY5ODA1\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrSNRqXGZxc1erUoHIuN00ds4qWutT1ichaBQ65U0QBohk9tKmI7CtzwfEvIa3Ir2qy2D4gd6wBuKA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次OpenAI给gpt-4o-mini-tts做了一个小小的功能演示网站，约等于免费给大家用了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还挺有意思的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7d3bd02f-66a3-4153-d81d-3edf15cde300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6685185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186141\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7d3bd02f-66a3-4153-d81d-3edf15cde300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://www.openai.fm/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最上面的VOICE是固定的音色，音色你是没办法克隆也没办法自定义的，所以只能选这些。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面的VIBE比较有意思，大概的意思就是情绪基调，有N多的预设模板，同时你也可以用Prompt自己捏。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI给了官方模板，是这个样子的：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"http\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">Voice</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:&nbsp;</span>High-energy, upbeat, and encouraging, projecting enthusiasm and motivation.&nbsp;</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">Punctuation</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:&nbsp;</span>Short, punchy sentences with strategic pauses to maintain excitement and clarity.</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">Delivery</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:&nbsp;</span>Fast-paced and dynamic, with rising intonation to build momentum and keep engagement high.&nbsp;</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">Phrasing</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:&nbsp;</span>Action-oriented and direct, using motivational cues to push participants forward.&nbsp;</span></code><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">Tone</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:&nbsp;</span>Positive, energetic, and empowering, creating an atmosphere of encouragement and achievement.</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">翻译过来就是：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"34\" data-end=\"76\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong data-start=\"34\" data-end=\"47\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">声音（Voice）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：充满活力、热情洋溢且积极鼓励，声音要能传递出热情与动力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"128\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong data-start=\"80\" data-end=\"99\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">标点（Punctuation）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：使用短小有力的句子，并通过适当停顿，保持兴奋感和清晰度。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"132\" data-end=\"182\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong data-start=\"132\" data-end=\"148\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">语速（Delivery）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：语速较快、富有变化，并用升调增加节奏感与吸引力，确保听众持续投入。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"186\" data-end=\"231\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong data-start=\"186\" data-end=\"202\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">措辞（Phrasing）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：直接明了、强调行动，使用鼓励性的语言来推动听众积极参与。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"273\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"247\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">语调（Tone）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：积极向上、充满能量与力量感，营造鼓励与成功的氛围。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我们是能看到，有5个可以自己去捏的参数。你可以随便自定义。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是这玩意，说实话写起来也非常麻烦，我试了一下后，不如直接交给AI，这玩意谁特么手搓啊= =</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/994ad5a6-22e8-4ee7-b8bc-3e7d82038500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6201456310679612\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"824\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186143\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/994ad5a6-22e8-4ee7-b8bc-3e7d82038500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">几秒钟，一段定制好的prompt就OK了，我们扔到之前的网页里。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/64ddf88b-450f-4f43-56b5-4ef5d8da3400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5305555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186144\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/64ddf88b-450f-4f43-56b5-4ef5d8da3400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再用一段我很喜欢的《反叛的鲁鲁修》里面的台词去试一下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-mpaudio class=\"js_editor_audio res_iframe js_uneditable custom_select_card\" data-pluginname=\"insertaudio\" name=\"openai-fm-sage-audio\" author=\"数字生命卡兹克\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/audio_tmpl&amp;name=openai-fm-sage-audio&amp;play_length=\" isaac2=\"0\" low_size=\"979.7\" source_size=\"979.7\" high_size=\"979.7\" play_length=\"20000\" data-trans_state=\"1\" data-verify_state=\"3\" voice_encode_fileid=\"MzIyMzA5NjEyMF8yNjQ3NjY5ODA2\" cover=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURrSNRqXGZxc1erUoHIuN00ds4qWutT1ichaBQ65U0QBohk9tKmI7CtzwfEvIa3Ir2qy2D4gd6wBuKA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\"></mp-common-mpaudio>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家自己判别吧。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在价格上，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-tts是$0.015/分钟，大概1毛钱人名币1分钟，说实话，已经几乎是最低价了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b88f633-1400-4095-f69e-63bcaaee6700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4388888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186146\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b88f633-1400-4095-f69e-63bcaaee6700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">11labs的价格大概是每分钟1块3人民币。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Minimax已经算是价格屠夫了，大概也要1毛8人民币1分钟。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/422f8e68-cb10-477a-ec85-456aee9cb500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38635294117647057\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186147\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/422f8e68-cb10-477a-ec85-456aee9cb500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">写在最后</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是OpenAI今天的发布了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你是开发者，想知道怎么接入，一切都在他们的API文档里。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/audio</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次还蛮方便的，10行代码就可以接了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">STT模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-transcribe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我还是蛮推荐用的，实测下来感觉性价比最高，差距不是很大，价格还低一半。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">TTS模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">gpt-4o-mini-tts</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你是做英文场景的语音，还是值得一用的，毕竟便宜是真便宜，效果也还不错，中文的话不推荐用，因为没法用，中文我还是无脑推荐Minimax的Audio模块，不仅中文效果好，性价比高，海外版还可以语音克隆。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://www.minimax.io/audio</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很久以前我也首发安利过一次，现在依然有效：</span><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647667095&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b7c79eed641ea11617e6371f1616049f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"30秒就能完美复刻你的声音，这就是当今最强的中文AI语音克隆。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">30秒就能完美复刻你的声音，这就是当今最强的中文AI语音克隆。</span></a></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以上就是这一次OpenAI的全部发布了，熬夜肝完，为大家带来最新鲜的实测。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">好了，我要去睡两小时了，预约的早上9点医院做手术</span><img data-src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/t/wx_fed/we-emoji/res/assets/newemoji/Hurt.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/t/wx_fed/we-emoji/res/assets/newemoji/Hurt.png\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">...</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家晚安~</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克、dongyi</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：wzglyay@gmail.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "评测 OpenAI gpt-4o 系列语音模型：STT 和 TTS，含实测和价格对比。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测 OpenAI gpt-4o 系列语音模型：STT 和 TTS，含实测和价格对比。",
  "summary": "文章对 OpenAI 最新发布的 gpt-4o 系列语音模型进行了详细评测，包括 gpt-4o-transcribe 和 gpt-4o-mini-transcribe 两款 STT 模型，以及 gpt-4o-mini-tts 一款 TTS 模型。作者通过实际案例测试了 STT 模型的语音转文本准确率，并与 Google 和 Anthropic 的同类产品进行对比。同时，对 TTS 模型的语音合成效果进行了评估，尤其关注中文发音质量，并与 11Labs 和 Minimax 的产品进行了对比。文章还介绍了 TTS 模型的情绪控制功能和 API 接入方式，最后对各模型的价格进行了对比分析，为开发者提供了选型参考。作者推荐在 STT 任务中使用 GPT-4o-mini-transcribe，英文 TTS 任务中使用 GPT-4o-mini-tts，中文 TTS 任务中使用 Minimax 的 Audio 模块。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GPT-4o-mini-transcribe 在性价比方面表现突出",
      "explanation": "在语音转文本任务中，该模型在准确率与 GPT-4o-transcribe 相差不大的情况下，价格降低一半，更具吸引力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GPT-4o-mini-tts 在英文语音合成方面效果良好，但中文发音有待提升",
      "explanation": "该模型在英文语音合成方面表现不错，价格也极具竞争力，但在中文发音方面存在明显问题，不推荐使用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "情绪控制功能为 TTS 模型带来更多可能性",
      "explanation": "GPT-4o-mini-tts 提供了情绪基调的自定义功能，允许用户通过 Prompt 控制语音的情感表达，但手动调整较为复杂，可借助 AI 自动生成。"
    }
  ],
